EXTRACTED VALUE: Not likely to win any new fans to the series but seasoned players should be satisfied. [Issue 14, p.94]
Boasting the largest cast of Marvel Characters ever assembled into a single game, Marvel Ultimate Alliance is a comic book fans dream game.
It's the perfect metaphor for the New Rare; solid, competent, but not brilliant or innovative.
Taking one part "Bionic Commando," one part "Starship Troopers," and one part action, Lost Planet results in an entertaining game.
